							],
							"documentation": "加减法共享数据基（AdditiveBase）。\n设计要点：\n1) 仅存储上三角 0 <= i <= j <= N，\n2) 一维数组紧凑存储，索引公式见 idx()。\n3) 加法直接读表；减法用恒等式 a - b = (a + b) - 2b 复用同一张表，\n即同一份数据同时服务加法与减法两种运算。",
							"attributes": [
								{
									"_type": "UMLAttribute",
									"_id": "AAAAAAGehzGaJfbfzH8=",
									"_parent": {
										"$ref": "AAAAAAGehzGZuvSwkrA="
									},
									"name": "N",
									"isStatic": true,
									"isLeaf": true,
									"type": "int",
									"isReadOnly": true,
									"defaultValue": "100"
								},
								{
									"_type": "UMLAttribute",
									"_id": "AAAAAAGehzGaJfbkDWQ=",
									"_parent": {
										"$ref": "AAAAAAGehzGZuvSwkrA="
									},
									"name": "table",
									"visibility": "private",
									"isLeaf": true,
									"type": "int",
									"multiplicity": "*",
									"isReadOnly": true
								}
							],
